    "long_instructions": "#Apply a Consistent Style to Both Web Pages\r\n\r\nYour goal is to style both HTML pages by generating and linking a CSS file based on your chosen mood board.\r\n\r\n**Don't have your own mood board?** Attach one from the `sample_mood_boards` folder to your chat with AI.\r\n\r\n:::details [Helpful Steps]\r\n1. Use AI to generate the CSS File\r\n2. Save and Link the Stylesheet\r\n3. Preview Your Work\r\n4. Save as Version 1\r\n:::",
